title: Audio-Technica AT-LP60-BT Fully Automatic Wireless Belt-Drive Stereo Turntable
description:
Cut the cord, keep the vinyl.

The AT-LP60-BT gives you all the great features of our popular AT-LP60 fully automatic belt-drive stereo turntable but with the added convenience of Bluetooth® wireless connectivity. So you can set up your turntable in one room and listen to it in another without having to run a bunch of cables. Up to eight different pairs of speakers, headphones or other devices that utilize Bluetooth® wireless technology can be stored in the AT-LP60-BT’s memory.

To learn more about the AT-LP60BT please visit our site: http://www.audio-technica.com/cms/turntables/d41892c53111caf9/index.html
